entry.summary: From a debugger's view, Let's explore the computer world! How does compiler, linker and debugger coordinate with each other around the program written in specific programming language? How does a debugger work? If we develop a debugger for go programming language, we must master go type system, runtime... and some Operating System internals. OK,…
